- on API call:
    - check dailyRemaining
        - if dailyRemaining not set:
            - set dailyRemaining = N, expires at midnight
            - allow API call
        - else
            - if dailyRemaining > 0:
                - allow API call
                - set dailyRemaining = dailyRemaining -1, expires at midnight
            - else
                - throw "exceeded API limit" error